edu.rit.image

Class ImageQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.image.ImageQueue
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ByteImageQueue, ColorImageQueue, GrayImageQueue

    public abstract class ImageQueue
extends Object
    Class ImageQueue is the abstract base class for a queue of pixel rows for an image. An image queue is constructed by the getImageQueue() method of class BilevelPngWriter, GrayPngWriter, IndexPngWriter, or ColorPngWriter.
    See Also:
    ByteImageQueue, ColorImageQueue, BilevelPngWriter, GrayPngWriter, IndexPngWriter, ColorPngWriter, ColorApngWriter
